    "content": "## Aider\n- Add GPT-5 models support\n- Add Grok-4 support\n- Add `gemini/gemini-2.5-flash-lite-preview-06-17` support\n- `/clear` prints success message\n- `/undo` shows first line of commit\n- Add `openrouter/moonshotai/kimi-k2` support\n- Display model announcements\n\n## Hugging Face Blog\n- Introduce NVIDIA NeMo Retriever pipeline\n- Announce Storage Buckets on Hub\n- Share lessons from 16 Open-Source RL libraries\n- Unveil Granite 4.0 1B Speech model\n\n## OpenAI SDK\n- Implement custom voices `api`\n- Update `api` and Sora `api` improvements\n- Repair merged videos resource\n- `GA ComputerTool` uses `CompuerTool` class\n- Move `computer_use_preview` to `ComputerUsePreview`\n- Add `gpt-5.4`, tool search, new computer tool\n- Remove `prompt_cache_key`, `phase` from responses\n- Add `gpt-realtime-1.5`, `gpt-audio-1.5` models\n- Implement websockets for responses `api`\n- Add `container network_policy`, `skills`\n- Resolve structured outputs memory leak\n- Preserve webhooks method visibility\n- Support images in batch `api`\n- Add `skills` and hosted shell\n\n## Claude Code\n- Add MCP elicitation support\n- Add Elicitation, ElicitationResult hooks\n- Add `-n`/`--name` CLI flag\n- Add `worktree.sparsePaths` setting\n- Pass `confirmed=true` for inline comments\n- Add actionable suggestions to `/context`\n- Add `autoMemoryDirectory` setting\n- Fix streaming API memory leak\n- Fix managed policy ask bypass\n- Add `modelOverrides` setting\n- Add OAuth, connectivity error guidance\n- Fix freezes from permission prompts\n- Fix deadlock from skill file changes\n- Change tool search bypass proxy\n- Add `w` key in `/copy` to write to file\n- Add optional description to `/plan`\n- Add `claude plugins` alias\n- Add `ExitWorktree` tool\n- Add `/loop` command\n- Add cron scheduling tools\n- Add `voice:pushToTalk` keybinding\n- Add bash auto-approval allowlist commands\n- Fix API 400 errors with `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL`\n- Fix API Error: 400 with custom model IDs\n- Fix empty model responses after ToolSearch\n- Add `/claude-api` skill\n- Add `Ctrl+U` to exit bash prompt\n- Add numeric keypad support\n- Add optional `name` to `/remote-control`\n- Set Opus 4.6 default to medium effort\n- Re-introduce \"ultrathink\" keyword\n- Remove Opus 4 and 4.1 from API\n\n## Ollama\n- Improve OpenClaw, Ollama cloud performance\n- Introduce Nemotron-3-Super model\n- Speed up Kimi-K2.5 by 2x\n- Improve tool calling accuracy\n- Ollama is now an OpenClaw provider\n- Interpret thinking levels\n- Add context length for compaction\n\n## Anthropic SDK\n- Clean up model enum list\n- GA `thinking-display-setting`\n- Add missing 413, 529 error handlers\n- Propagate `container_id` for tool calling\n- Use filtered messages in async compaction\n- Change `array_format` to `brackets`\n- Add conversion helpers for MCP tools\n- Add top-level cache control\n- Fix shared `UserLocation`, error types\n- Add backward-compat aliases\n- New tool versions as top-level types\n- Release `claude-sonnet-4-6`\n- Fix spec errors\n- Remove `speed` from GA messages\n- Enable `fast-mode` in `claude-opus-4-6`\n- Pass `speed` parameter through\n- Release Claude Opus 4.6, adaptive thinking\n- Send structured output beta header\n- Support Structured Outputs in Messages API\n- Migrate sending message format\n- Add custom JSON encoder\n\n## Last Week in AI Summary\n- Podcast #237: Nemotron 3 Super, xAI reborn\n- #338: Anthropic sues Trump, xAI starting over\n- Podcast #236: GPT 5.4, Gemini 3.1 Flash Lite\n\n## Latent Space Summary\n- AINews: Context Drought\n- AINews: Raise aspirations for LLMs\n- Turbopuffer: Retrieval After RAG\n- AINews: Replit Agent 4\n- AINews: Yann LeCun's AMI Labs\n- NVIDIA's AI Engineers: Agent Inference\n- AINews: Autoresearch, Self Improvement\n\n## Gemini CLI\n- Update theme screenshots, add themes\n- Rename 'return' key to 'enter'\n- Restrict npm bundling\n- Override `toolRegistry` for sub-agents\n- Space footer items equally\n- Clarify global policy rules\n- Add chat resume footer\n- Support bold, styles in svg snapshots\n- Increase A2A agent timeout\n- Standardize semantic focus colors\n- Whitelist `TERM`, `COLORTERM`\n- Fix overage strategy lifecycle\n- Expand paste placeholders\n- Add in-memory cache to `ChatRecordingService`\n- Overhaul thinking UI\n- Unify `Ctrl+O` expansion hint\n- Update model docs\n- Fix typo in documentation\n- Add Windows PowerShell equivalents\n- Parse raw ASCII buffer strings\n- Use robot PAT for automated PRs"
  }
]